        logger.info("Dependency sweep [%s]: %d suggestions, %d findings", ...)
except TimeoutError:
    logger.error("Dependency sweep timed out for user %s (300s limit)", user_label)
except Exception:
    logger.exception("Dependency sweep failed for user %s", user_label)
```

**After**: `await _run_dependency_sweep_for_user(user_id, user_label)` — one line at each call site.

